{"word":"嗌","detail":[{"title":"基本字义解释","content":[[{"type":"text","content":"● "},{"type":"strong","content":"嗌"},{"type":"span","content":"yìㄧˋ","class":["pinyin"]}],[{"type":"text","content":"◎ 咽喉。"}],[{"type":"text","content":"● "},{"type":"strong","content":"嗌"},{"type":"span","content":"àiㄞˋ","class":["pinyin"]}],[{"type":"text","content":"◎ 〔"},{"type":"span","content":"嗌嗌","class":["fontred"]},{"type":"text","content":"〕笑声，如“一幸得胜，疾笑"},{"type":"span","content":"嗌嗌","class":["fontred"]},{"type":"text","content":"”。"}],[{"type":"text","content":"◎ 咽喉窒塞，噎。"}]]},{"title":"英文翻译","content":[[{"type":"text","content":"the throat; to quarrel, choke"}]]},{"title":"详细字义解释","content":[[{"type":"text","content":"◎ "},{"type":"strong","content":"嗌"},{"type":"text","content":" "},{"type":"span","content":"ài","class":["pinyin"]},{"type":"text","content":" "},{"type":"img","content":"","class":["sound"]},{"type":"text","content":" "}],[{"type":"span","content":"〈动词〉","class":["parts"]}],[{"type":"text","content":"(1) 咽喉塞住"},{"type":"br","content":""},{"type":"text","content":"嗌,噎也…秦晋或曰嗌。——《方言》"},{"type":"br","content":""},{"type":"text","content":"嗌不容粒。——《谷梁传·昭公十九年》。"}],[{"type":"text","content":"(2) 又如:嗌喉(上吊身亡)"}],[{"type":"text","content":"(3)  另见 "},{"type":"span","content":"yì","class":["pinyin"]},{"type":"text","content":" "},{"type":"img","content":"","class":["sound"]},{"type":"text","content":" "}]]},{"title":"基本词义解释","content":[[{"type":"text","content":"◎ "},{"type":"strong","content":"嗌"},{"type":"text","content":" "},{"type":"span","content":"yì","class":["pinyin"]},{"type":"text","content":" "},{"type":"img","content":"","class":["sound"]},{"type":"text","content":" "}],[{"type":"span","content":"〈名词〉","class":["parts"]}],[{"type":"text","content":"(1)  咽喉"},{"type":"br","content":""},{"type":"text","content":"咽,又谓之嗌,气所流通,厄要之处也。——《释名》"},{"type":"br","content":""},{"type":"text","content":"食之已嗌痛。——《山海经·北山经》"},{"type":"br","content":""},{"type":"text","content":"使我嗌疾而腰急。——《列子·汤问》"},{"type":"br","content":""},{"type":"text","content":"嗌于面尘,身无膏泽。——《素问》"}],[{"type":"text","content":"(2)  喻指交通要道"},{"type":"br","content":""},{"type":"text","content":"嗌者,扼也,扼要之处也。——《说文解字注》"}],[{"type":"text","content":"(3)  嗌喔。如:嗌呕(嗌喔。形容奉承取媚的声音)"}],[{"type":"text","content":"(4)  另见 "},{"type":"span","content":"ài","class":["pinyin"]},{"type":"text","content":" "},{"type":"img","content":"","class":["sound"]},{"type":"text","content":" "}]]},{"title":"康熙字典","content":[[{"type":"text","content":"【丑集上】【口字部】嗌 ·康熙筆画：13　·部外筆画：10 "}],[{"type":"text","content":"【唐韻】【集韻】【韻會】【正韻】"},{"type":"span","content":"𠀤"},{"type":"text","content":"伊昔切，音益。【說文】咽也。【穀梁傳·昭十九年】歠飦粥嗌，不容粒。【註】嗌，喉也。【楚辭·大招】四酎幷孰，不歰嗌只。【史記·倉公傳】飮食下嗌。【老子·道德經】終日號而嗌不嗄。　又【集韻】乙革切，音戹。義同。【莊子·大宗師】屈服者，其嗌言若哇。【釋文】嗌，郭音厄。　又【集韻】乙角切，音渥。笑也。【韓詩外傳】疾笑嗌嗌，威儀固陋。　又【集韻】烏懈切，音隘。【揚子·方言】嗌，噎也。秦晉或曰嗌，又曰噎。【註】皆謂咽痛。　又【集韻】壹計切，音翳。與齸同。江東名咽爲齸。"}]]},{"title":"说文解字","content":[[{"type":"text","content":"【卷二】【口部】"},{"type":"span","content":"嗌","class":["kszi"]}],[{"type":"text","content":"咽也。从口益聲。籒文嗌上象口，下象頸脈理也。伊昔切〖注〗《玉篇》"},{"type":"span","content":"𡁐"},{"type":"text","content":"，籒文嗌。又"},{"type":"span","content":"䒣"},{"type":"text","content":"，同苒。草盛貌。"}]]},{"title":"字源演变","content":[]},{"title":"同音字","content":[]}],"type":"通用字","pinyin":["ài","yì"],"radical":"口","stroke":"十画","total_stroke":"十三画","stroke_order":"丨フ一丶ノ一ノ丶丨フ丨丨一","input_method":{"bopomofo":"RTCT","number":"68012","unicode":"U+55CC","wubi":"KUWL"}}